{"tid":494822,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"老老實實，就算C朗拎一萬次金球獎","createTime":"2017-12-10T05:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-10T12:30:48.000Z","uid":72652,"like":145,"dislike":82,"uniUserReply":40,"replies":[{"pid":"961da73cdddcf67b8b7f591336822127671d4473","tid":494822,"uid":72652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:47:58.000Z","msg":"佢都冇可能成為球王<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n根本係踢法問題<br />\n以前德國轟炸機梅拿又係入勁多波<br />\n年度入球紀錄到近年先比美斯破左<br />\n<br />\n但你問十個唔熟足球的人<br />\n十個都唔識梅拿<br />\n<br />\n反而佢地識比利 老馬 施丹<br />\n<br />\n根本要carry一隊波<br />\n冇可能只係企最前線等人供應<br />\n隊波狀況一差 就自動收皮<br />\n你睇下今屆皇馬<br />\n<br />\n踢開街場都知<br />\n最好波的一定係擺佢係中後場carry全隊<br />\n<br />\n再者<br />\n「the best player in history 」應該係人地賦予比你<br />\n唔係你自己講多幾次就會成真<br />\n<br />\n當全世界都拎美斯同比利 老馬比<br />\n而C朗仲係同緊美斯比<br />\n就日日話自己係史上最佳<br />\n<br />\n知唔知醜呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n都未計 爭射單刀/插水/打人/no look pass 個堆唔應該發生係球王身上的柒野<br />\n<br />\n係呀 4:1 追成 5:5係好勁<br />\n我都覺得呢種毅力好值得欣賞<br />\n<br />\n但係咁代表咩？<br />\n代表你做緊的野人地做到好耐囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfc1b7a80b7942f1e531716d53833e3bbb629a6e","tid":494822,"uid":126314,"like":65,"dislike":26,"score":39,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T05:58:00.000Z","msg":"得啦得啦 收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e551c242873489aa157d08808142821347713711","tid":494822,"uid":35176,"like":6,"dislike":6,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:04:05.000Z","msg":"唔會 C朗已經係歷史第一（自封）<br />\n想反駁？ 請問在座有邊位比C朗識波？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n梗係無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  所以C朗歷史第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a622e0e028c49b528698b6b3967d62f5d65fe0","tid":494822,"uid":90422,"like":33,"dislike":6,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:04:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得啦得啦 收皮啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 駁唔到發爛渣"},{"pid":"a27ceb822046345b8af5bdbc87ad5238d840bfef","tid":494822,"uid":33497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:05:12.000Z","msg":"好似幾啱"},{"pid":"a84ed5ed2b2e6bf3cd5acdc95010d8290d609c56","tid":494822,"uid":90422,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:05:36.000Z","msg":"c朗自己講自己係最佳就得<br />\n我地開po討論就唔得<br />\n朗迷真係大撚晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d6a8133e87232b29e4575634713d89530d186a9","tid":494822,"uid":106701,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:06:42.000Z","msg":"酸"},{"pid":"dfd6472293cdc2d8d04d332f1bf0eaefb9940f43","tid":494822,"uid":144691,"like":32,"dislike":4,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:11:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n但你問十個唔熟足球的人<br />\n十個都唔識梅拿<br />\n<br />\n反而佢地識比利 老馬 施丹<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n宜家十個唔熟足球嘅人 都有起碼七八個識牙朗啦<br />\n拎梅拿嚟比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n洗唔洗咁酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c934c3a2849d3f60c8b25b761a99d8e9fa9f1776","tid":494822,"uid":21970,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T06:14:36.000Z","msg":"拎街場比 咁派路先係唯一球王啦<br />\n再者<br />\n小朋友可能冇睇過老馬踢波<br />\n講脾氣呀朗邊夠佢黎"},{"pid":"5e4ae4fc719b8cd6a6846799495a